                    <span>Im building a 4,20 (15feet)International class sailboat using epoxies and 4mm plywood using Van de stadt plans. And because I wanted to check it I order this book.<BR>Im very disappointed ! The calculations does not work in small boats Are Completely Wrong! <BR>Author mentioning that the calculations can be used from 3 meters boats to 37 meter boats .But when I tried the results was a 6 times thicker boat !<BR>Do not hesitate to contact me if you thing Im wrong</span>
                  
